{"body": "<p>I was missing the version at the end of the URL (<code>1.3.2</code> in that case).</p>\n\n<p>The final update site URL (in \"Help -> Install New Software\") was: <code>http://download.eclipse.org/bpmn2-modeler/updates/neon/1.3.2/</code></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/WH1rD.png\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/WH1rD.png\" alt=\"Correct update site URL for Eclipse Neon&#39;s BPMN2-Modeler plugin\"></a></p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Note that <a href=\"https://eclipse.org/graphiti/download.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Graphiti</a> also provides BPMN2-Modeler plugin in his Graphiti update site for Neon: <code>http://download.eclipse.org/releases/neon</code>.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/jHKlM.png\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/jHKlM.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Graphiti download instructions\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/iBTiE.png\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/iBTiE.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Graphiti - BPMN2-Modeler plugin available\"></a></p>\n", "tags": ["java", "eclipse", "eclipse-plugin", "bpmn"], "creation_date": 1477566181, "score": 0, "last_activity_date": 1477566181, "answer_id": 40282981, "is_accepted": false, "owner": {"user_id": 759452, "reputation": 6672, "user_type": "registered", "accept_rate": 60, "display_name": "Adrien Be", "link": "http://stackoverflow.com/users/759452/adrien-be", "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/61f287ce4e27eaa06b91354713ebd3e7?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG"}, "title": "Install eclipse plugin BPMN2-Modeler", "question_id": 40282550}